---

<BaseLayout title="Book Your Free Trial - Be More Free">
  <!-- Hero Section with Dynamic Gradient -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[45vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Animated gradient background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 via-primary-700 to-accent-600"></div>
    
    <!-- Geometric patterns -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-white rounded-full mix-blend-overlay filter blur-3xl animate-float"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-accent-300 rounded-full mix-blend-overlay filter blur-3xl animate-float" style="animation-delay: 3s;"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center relative z-10 py-20">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        Tried <span class="text-accent-300">EVERYTHING?</span><br />
        Look For Yourself And <br />Maybe <span class="text-accent-300">Change Your Life</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Years of therapies with nothing much to show for it? The Neutral Zone process 
        helps you find real answers in hours, not years‚Äîwithout someone else's agenda.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="#booking-form" 
           class="group bg-white text-primary-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-bold hover:bg-accent-400 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-2xl">
          Book Your Free 30-Minute Session
          <span class="inline-block ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">‚Üí</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/neutral-zone" 
           class="bg-transparent text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-bold border-2 border-white/50 hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white transition-all duration-300">
          How It Works
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem/Solution Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">
            Stop <span class="text-red-500">Wasting Time</span> on What Doesn't Work
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
            You've tried everything, but you're still struggling with the same problems
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-red-200">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-red-900">What You've Been Doing</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-red-500 mr-3 text-xl">‚úó</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Years of weekly therapy sessions</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-red-500 mr-3 text-xl">‚úó</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Endless coping mechanisms to manage</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-red-500 mr-3 text-xl">‚úó</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Being told what your problems "really" mean</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-red-500 mr-3 text-xl">‚úó</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Following someone else's framework</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-red-500 mr-3 text-xl">‚úó</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Still stuck with the same issues</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-green-200">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-green-900">What Actually Works</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-3 text-xl">‚úì</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Find your own answers in hours</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-3 text-xl">‚úì</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Actually resolve issues, not manage them</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-3 text-xl">‚úì</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Your truth is taken as truth, period</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-3 text-xl">‚úì</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700">No one's agenda but your own</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-3 text-xl">‚úì</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Real freedom from what's been holding you back</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
            It's time to try something that <span class="text-primary-600">actually works</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Neutral Zone Process - Clickable Cards -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 relative">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">
          The <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-500">Neutral Zone</span> Process
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          A radically different approach that helps you be more free
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        {neutralZonePrinciples.map((item, index) => (
          <a href={`/principles/${item.slug}`} class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden cursor-pointer">
            <!-- Gradient overlay on hover -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-accent-50 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
            
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-3">{item.icon}</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 group-hover:text-primary-700 transition-colors">
                {item.title}
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                {item.description}
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-center text-primary-600 group-hover:text-primary-700 font-medium text-sm">
                Learn more
                <span class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">‚Üí</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works - Visual Process -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">
        How to <span class="text-accent-500">Be More Free</span>
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="relative inline-block mb-6">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-4xl font-black shadow-xl group-hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow">
              1
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Book a Free Trial</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Experience the Neutral Zone process with a free 30-minute session. 
            No commitment, no pressure.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="relative inline-block mb-6">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500 to-accent-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-4xl font-black shadow-xl group-hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow">
              2
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Explore What's There</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            In a completely neutral space, examine whatever you want to look at. 
            Your pace, your direction.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="relative inline-block mb-6">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-accent-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-4xl font-black shadow-xl group-hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow">
              3
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Make Your Own Choices</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Discover your own truth and decide what to do with it. 
            No one else's agenda‚Äîjust yours.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials with Modern Cards -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-center text-gray-900 mb-3">
        Real People. <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-500">Real Freedom.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        They stopped being stuck and started being free
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        {testimonials.map((testimonial, index) => (
          <div class="group relative">
            <!-- Background card -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-accent-100 rounded-2xl transform rotate-2 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
            
            <!-- Main card -->
            <div class="relative bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
              <div class="mb-4">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-accent-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic">
                {testimonial.quote}
              </p>
              <div class="border-t pt-3">
                <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">{testimonial.author}</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">{testimonial.role}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Booking Form Section -->
  <section id="booking-form" class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 via-primary-700 to-accent-600"></div>
    
    <!-- Animated shapes -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-64 h-64 bg-white rounded-full mix-blend-overlay filter blur-3xl animate-float"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-accent-300 rounded-full mix-blend-overlay filter blur-3xl animate-float" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center relative z-10">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6">
        Ready to Stop Being Stuck?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Your first 30-minute Neutral Zone session is free. Find out what happens 
        when you have actual space to look at what's keeping you stuck.
      </p>
      
      <!-- Cal.com embed placeholder - TODO: Integrate with actual Cal.com -->
        <!-- Placeholder for Cal.com widget -->
        <div class="bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Book Your Free 30-Minute Session</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Choose a time that works for you. Sessions are conducted via phone, Google Meet, or Zoom.
          </p>
          
          <button 
             data-cal-link="be-more-free/30min"
             data-cal-namespace="30min"
             data-cal-config='{"layout":"month_view"}'
             class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 inline-flex items-center cursor-pointer">
            Open Booking Calendar
            <span class="ml-2">‚Üí</span>
          </button>
          
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-6">
            <strong>Note:</strong> The Neutral Zone process is not therapy, counseling, or medical treatment. 
            It's a different approach to examining your own material in a neutral space.
          </p>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section with Expandable Cards -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">
        Common <span class="text-accent-500">Questions</span>
      </h2>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow p-6 border-l-4 border-primary-500">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center">
            <span class="text-primary-500 mr-3">‚Ä¢</span>
            Is this therapy?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            No. The Neutral Zone process is not therapy, counseling, or medical treatment. 
            It's a completely different approach where you explore your own material 
            without evaluation or interpretation from anyone else.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow p-6 border-l-4 border-accent-500">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center">
            <span class="text-accent-500 mr-3">‚Ä¢</span>
            How is this different from coaching?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Coaches typically guide you toward goals and offer strategies. 
            In Neutral Zone sessions, the facilitator offers no guidance, advice, or direction. 
            You find your own answers in a truly neutral space.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow p-6 border-l-4 border-primary-500">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center">
            <span class="text-primary-500 mr-3">‚Ä¢</span>
            What if I don't know what to talk about?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            That's perfectly fine. You can explore that feeling itself, or anything else 
            that comes up. There's no wrong way to use your time in the Neutral Zone.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="/neutral-zone" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-bold text-lg inline-flex items-center group">
          Learn more about the Neutral Zone process
          <span class="ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">‚Üí</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
